10
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:50,000
I'm going to the bathroom.

11
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:52,960
You're taking your bag to the bathroom?

12
00:00:53,680 --> 00:00:54,680
Chu...

13
00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:55,440
What did you just call me?

14
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:57,960
Babe.

15
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:01,040
I'm really fine now.

16
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:01,880
I've been here too long.

17
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:02,680
Listen to me.

18
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:03,880
Let's keep you here a little longer, just to be safe.

19
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:04,920
I protest.

20
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:06,320
Protest denied.

21
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:12,280
You're staying right here.

22
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:13,320
Don't even think about sneaking out.

23
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:21,080
Hey, Jiayang. What's up?

24
00:01:21,080 --> 00:01:22,680
Lucky you, you're in for a treat again.

25
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:24,120
What are you talking about?

26
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:24,760
He Zheng,

27
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,760
I made a few of my specialties.

28
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:28,280
I'll bring them over later.

29
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:30,440
What now?

30
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:31,320
We already ate.

31
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:33,240
Jiayang, Qian.

32
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:34,560
I really appreciate it,

33
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:36,480
but Xi and I have already eaten.

34
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:38,360
You don't need to make a special trip.

35
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:39,560
Go ahead and eat without us.

36
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:41,280
It's no trouble at all.

37
00:01:41,440 --> 00:01:43,160
We're already at the hospital entrance.

38
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:44,960
I...

39
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:46,440
What should we do?

40
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,880
Didn't you say you were going crazy stuck here?

41
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:48,280
Yeah.

42
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:48,960
Let's go.

43
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:49,760
Okay.

44
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,840
Qian, no need to rush.

45
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,680
You bought watermelon and even cooked for them.

46
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,880
You really don't have to rush.

47
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,840
That's my business.

48
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:03,440
Easy.

49
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:04,440
- The food's getting cold. - They should still be here.

50
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:07,600
Where to?

51
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:08,440
This way.

52
00:02:09,630 --> 00:02:10,320
I gotta say...

53
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:12,160
Qian, you're the thoughtful one.

54
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,280
Two watermelons would've been enough.

55
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,440
You even cooked for them.

56
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,160
Mind your own business.

57
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:17,280
Alright. Take it slow.

58
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,760
Slow down.

59
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:19,280
Hey, knock it off.

60
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,440
Enough talking, walk faster.

61
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,040
Okay.

62
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:26,840
Did they leave?

63
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,760
Looks like it.

64
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,480
What are you two doing?

65
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:56,760
Where are they?

66
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,640
I'll give him a call.

67
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:06,560
[Something urgent came up, had to go.]
He Zheng texted. He and Xi left.

68
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,920
That's a bit much.

69
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,720
What could be so urgent they couldn't even stay for a meal?

70
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:13,040
Feels like our effort went to waste.

71
00:03:14,220 --> 00:03:15,820
[The ward's still booked, perfect for a date. Make your move, bro.]

72
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,560
What did He Zheng say this time?

73
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,320
He said...

74
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,120
He said he was really sorry.

75
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:26,240
Did he say where they went?

76
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,280
No.

77
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:32,040
It's just...

78
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,080
all this food,

79
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:34,200
if we throw it out,

80
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,560
that'd be such a waste.

81
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,760
How about...

82
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:42,280
the two of us

83
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,400
finish it?

84
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,920
That works.

85
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:47,000
Alright.

86
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,960
Let's just finish it ourselves.

87
00:03:53,820 --> 00:03:56,460
